The '''Aranara Series''' ''(unofficial name)'' is a 4-star [[Weapon Series]].

This series can be [[Forging|forged]] and all weapons of the series require [[Midlander Billets]] to be forged.

Only [[Forest Regalia]] and [[Sapwood Blade]] share the same ability bonus.
